Package: consort2
Type: Package
Title: Create Consort Diagram
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: person("Alim", "Dayim",
                  email = "ad938@cam.ac.uk",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9998-7463"))
Description: A modern, simplified framework for creating CONSORT (Consolidated
    Standards of Reporting Trials) diagrams for the transparent reporting of
    participant allocation in randomized, controlled clinical trials. Provides a
    declarative API for building diagrams with full styling control, supporting
    both Graphviz and grid rendering backends.
